<h3 class="break-bold">Our Purpose</h3>

<div class="paragraph">Our goal is to teach you the process of coming up with amazing and creative ideas. The Imagination Team has created tutorials to help you think about how to make clever solutions to all types of problems. Our team is comprised of USI Seniors of IT Management, Computer Science, and Graphic Design. With the help of the USI Faculty we have collected and displayed the cutting edge of the Ideation process. Using this process has changed the lives of so many as creative solutions make life easier or push the limits of what can be. The Success Stories of using our method have near infinite possibilities. Following our guide will help you come up with ideas for all the problems you might face. We have also got in touch with Local Evansville Businesses to give us some real corporate problems that need your help. Evansville Regional Airport is offering cash and employment rewards for those who can solve their toughest challenge yet. Head to our Featured challenge page to get more information.</div>

<h3 class="break-bold">Dr. Khayum's Vision</h3>
<div class="form-horizontal">
    <div class="form-group">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="paragraph">The Imagination Portal is the product of Dr. Mohammed Khayum's (USI's Dean of the Romain College of Business) vision. Dr. Khayum had the idea to create a medium for the students of USI to generate and submit ideas on how to better the college community. He wanted to give students the tools and means to generate innovative ideas. Through this website, his imagination process can be captured and shared through the Imagination Steps!</div>
            
